To setup a wine bottle with a complete Unity runtime, run:

unity-bottler install

To then run Unity, execute:

unity-bottler

To remove the wine bottle, run:

unity-bottler remove

To configure the wine bottle, run:

unity-bottler configure

Note: If you ever get signed out, go to unity-bottler configure < Run Unity 2017.4.40f1 to get signed in again.
